Date of Birth: November 7, 1900<br/>
Birthplace: Salt Lake City, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: April 20, 1944<br/>
Death:Jan. 11, 1984<br/>
<br/>
Born Nov. 7, 1900, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, to Christian Petersen and Christine M. Andersen.
Ordained apostle April 20, 1944, by Heber J. Grant, at age 43; died Jan. 11, 1984, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 83.